title: Grateful Dead Live at Henry J. Kaiser Convention Center on 1988-03-17
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket-> Sugaree, Minglewood Blues, Ramble On Rose, Memphis Blues, Row Jimmy, Let It Grow

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums*-> Big Boss Man-> Jam-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> I Need A Miracle-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Hey Jude Reprise, E: Black Muddy River

*W/ Hamza El Din
